N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4404.6 - Food and beverages

State Regulations

No food or beverages may be sold, served or consumed, nor
merchandise of any kind sold by vending machine or otherwise in the public area
of any branch office without the prior approval of the
commission. Notes
